document_data.name: Daftar
document_data.mainbody: A '''daftar''' was a [[Zakharan]] sea captain's most treasured item.
document_data.Uses: Daftar comprised instructions, tables, charts, etc. compiled over years of sailing the seas of the Land of Fate. A captain without their daftar found himself at a sad disadvantage while at sea. They were often jealously guarded and could never be purchased.
